    "body_html": "<div class=\"slide-root\"><style>.slide-root{background:var(--color-bg);font-family:var(--font-body);}.pol-header{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:520px;height:100%;background:var(--color-primary);display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:60px 50px 60px 60px;box-sizing:border-box;}.pol-header .sec-label{font-family:var(--font-en);font-size:var(--text-label);color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px;}.pol-header .sec-title{font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-display);color:#fff;line-height:1.25;margin-bottom:24px;}.pol-header .sec-sub{font-size:var(--text-body);color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);line-height:1.7;}.pol-header .doc-tag{display:inline-block;margin-top:32px;padding:6px 18px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.35);border-radius:4px;font-size:var(--text-caption);color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);letter-spacing:1px;}.pol-body{position:absolute;top:0;left:520px;right:0;height:100%;padding:54px 64px 48px 64px;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column;}.pol-body .topic-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:28px;}.topic-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--color-accent);flex-shrink:0;}.topic-text{font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-h3);color:var(--color-text-primary);}.card-grid{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px;flex:1;}.pol-card{background:var(--color-surface);border-radius:var(--border-radius);padding:22px 28px;display:flex;gap:22px;align-items:flex-start;border-left:4px solid var(--color-accent);}.pol-card .card-icon{flex-shrink:0;width:44px;height:44px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}.pol-card .card-icon svg{width:32px;height:32px;}.pol-card .card-content{flex:1;}.pol-card .card-title{font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-h3);color:var(--color-text-primary);margin-bottom:6px;}.pol-card .card-desc{font-size:var(--text-body);color:var(--color-text-secondary);line-height:1.65;}.pol-card .card-ref{font-size:var(--text-caption);color:var(--color-accent);margin-top:8px;display:inline-block;}.footer-note{margin-top:auto;padding-top:16px;border-top:1px solid var(--color-border);font-size:var(--text-caption);color:var(--color-text-secondary);line-height:1.6;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;}.footer-note .fn-icon{flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;}</style><div class=\"pol-header\"><svg style=\"position:absolute;top:-60px;right:-80px;width:320px;height:320px;opacity:.08\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 320\"><circle cx=\"160\" cy=\"160\" r=\"150\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><circle cx=\"160\" cy=\"160\" r=\"110\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"160\" cy=\"160\" r=\"70\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\".8\"/></svg><svg style=\"position:absolute;bottom:40px;left:20px;width:200px;height:200px;opacity:.06\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 200\"><rect x=\"20\" y=\"20\" width=\"160\" height=\"160\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"1\" transform=\"rotate(15 100 100)\"/><rect x=\"40\" y=\"40\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\".8\" transform=\"rotate(15 100 100)\"/></svg><span class=\"sec-label\">Background Research</span><h1 class=\"sec-title\">国家政策<br>解读</h1><p class=\"sec-sub\">CJJ14-2016《城市公共厕所设计标准》对二类及以上公厕提出刚性技术要求，直接约束本项目设计方案。</p><span class=\"doc-tag\">CJJ14-2016 · 住建部</span></div><div class=\"pol-body\"><div class=\"topic-bar\"><span class=\"topic-dot\"></span><span class=\"topic-text\">二类以上公厕刚性要求条目</span></div><div class=\"card-grid\"><div class=\"pol-card\"><div class=\"card-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\"><rect x=\"4\" y=\"6\" width=\"24\" height=\"20\" rx=\"3\" stroke=\"var(--color-accent)\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><path d=\"M11 16h10M11 20h6\" stroke=\"var(--color-accent)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"16\" cy=\"11\" r=\"2\" stroke=\"var(--color-accent)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-content\"><div class=\"card-title\">第三卫生间（家庭卫生间）</div><div class=\"card-desc\">二类及以上公厕须设置独立第三卫生间，配备成人及儿童坐便器、安全抓杆、婴儿护理台和呼叫按钮，面积不小于 6.5 m²，满足异性陪护、老幼及残障人士如厕需求。</div><span class=\"card-ref\">依据：CJJ14-2016 第 5.3 节</span></div></div><div class=\"pol-card\"><div class=\"card-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"16\" cy=\"12\" r=\"5\" stroke=\"var(--color-accent)\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><path d=\"M8 28c0-4.4 3.6-8 8-8s8 3.6 8 8\" stroke=\"var(--color-accent)\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M22 12l4 4M22 16l4-4\" stroke=\"var(--color-accent)\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\".5\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-content\"><div class=\"card-title\">无障碍设施配置</div><div class=\"card-desc\">须设置无障碍厕位（≥1 个）及无障碍通道，门宽≥ 800 mm、地面防滑系数≥ 0.6，厕位内配低位洗手盆、L 型安全扶手及紧急呼叫装置，轮椅回转直径≥ 1500 mm。</div><span class=\"card-ref\">依据：CJJ14-2016 第 5.4 节 / GB 50763</span></div></div><div class=\"pol-card\"><div class=\"card-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 22c2-6 6-10 10-10s8 4 10 10\" stroke=\"var(--color-accent)\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M16 6v4M10 8l2 3M22 8l-2 3\" stroke=\"var(--color-accent)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><line x1=\"4\" y1=\"26\" x2=\"28\" y2=\"26\" stroke=\"var(--color-accent)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-content\"><div class=\"card-title\">通风除臭系统</div><div class=\"card-desc\">二类公厕臭气浓度须≤ 1 级，要求独立机械通风系统，换气次数≥ 5 次/h；宜采用负压排风+活性炭/光催化除臭组合工艺，排风口高于屋面 1.5 m 以上，确保室内氨浓度≤ 1.0 mg/m³。</div><span class=\"card-ref\">依据：CJJ14-2016 第 6.2 节</span></div></div></div><div class=\"footer-note\"><span class=\"fn-icon\"><svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"7\" cy=\"7\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"var(--color-text-secondary)\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><path d=\"M7 4v3.5M7 9.5v.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-text-secondary)\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><span>以上条目为十堰市公厕改造项目的刚性设计约束，后续方案须逐条对标落实。完整标准文本参见住建部官网 CJJ14-2016 公告。</span></div></div></div>",
