    "body_html": "<div class=\"slide-root\"><style>.slide-root{background:var(--color-bg);font-family:var(--font-body);}.pi-header{position:absolute;top:60px;left:80px;z-index:10;}.pi-header .section-label{font-family:var(--font-en);font-size:var(--text-label);color:var(--color-text-secondary);letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;}.pi-header h1{font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-h1);color:var(--color-text-primary);margin:0;line-height:1.3;}.pi-header .subtitle{font-size:var(--text-body);color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-top:10px;max-width:500px;line-height:1.7;}.pi-matrix-area{position:absolute;top:60px;right:80px;width:960px;height:620px;}.pi-matrix{width:100%;height:100%;position:relative;}.pi-axis-y{position:absolute;left:0;top:40px;bottom:60px;width:44px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}.pi-axis-y-label{writing-mode:vertical-rl;text-orientation:mixed;font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-caption);color:var(--color-text-secondary);letter-spacing:4px;}.pi-axis-x{position:absolute;bottom:10px;left:60px;right:20px;text-align:center;font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-caption);color:var(--color-text-secondary);letter-spacing:4px;}.pi-grid{position:absolute;top:20px;left:60px;right:20px;bottom:50px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;grid-template-rows:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;}.pi-cell{border-radius:var(--border-radius);padding:24px 22px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-start;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}.pi-cell-q1{background:rgba(var(--color-primary-rgb,76,107,98),0.08);border:1.5px solid rgba(var(--color-primary-rgb,76,107,98),0.18);}.pi-cell-q2{background:var(--color-accent);border:1.5px solid var(--color-accent);}.pi-cell-q3{background:rgba(var(--color-primary-rgb,76,107,98),0.04);border:1px dashed var(--color-border);}.pi-cell-q4{background:rgba(var(--color-primary-rgb,76,107,98),0.06);border:1.5px solid rgba(var(--color-primary-rgb,76,107,98),0.12);}.pi-cell-tag{font-family:var(--font-en);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:0.6;}.pi-cell h3{font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-h3);margin:0 0 8px 0;line-height:1.4;}.pi-cell p{font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;margin:0;color:var(--color-text-secondary);}.pi-cell-q2 h3,.pi-cell-q2 p,.pi-cell-q2 .pi-cell-tag{color:#fff;}.pi-cell-q2 p{opacity:0.88;}.pi-cell-q2 .pi-cell-tag{opacity:0.7;}.pi-star{position:absolute;top:12px;right:14px;font-size:18px;}.pi-bottom{position:absolute;bottom:50px;left:80px;width:820px;display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:stretch;}.pi-conclusion{flex:1;background:var(--color-surface);border-left:4px solid var(--color-accent);border-radius:var(--border-radius);padding:22px 28px;}.pi-conclusion h4{font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-h3);color:var(--color-text-primary);margin:0 0 8px 0;}.pi-conclusion p{font-size:var(--text-body);color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin:0;line-height:1.75;}.pi-arrow-col{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:48px;flex-shrink:0;}.pi-deco-line{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:4px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--color-primary),var(--color-accent),transparent);}</style><div class=\"pi-header\"><div class=\"section-label\">Background Research</div><h1>政策影响总结</h1><p class=\"subtitle\">国家标准划定功能底线，省市规划驱动品质升级——双重逻辑交汇，明确项目核心方向。</p></div><div class=\"pi-matrix-area\"><div class=\"pi-matrix\"><div class=\"pi-axis-y\"><span class=\"pi-axis-y-label\">品质升级 →</span></div><div class=\"pi-axis-x\">功能合规 →</div><div class=\"pi-grid\"><div class=\"pi-cell pi-cell-q1\"><span class=\"pi-cell-tag\">Q2 · 省市规划驱动</span><h3>文化生态品质升级</h3><p>十堰市文旅融合规划要求公共文化建筑承载地域文化表达，融入生态景观体系，提升城市文化辨识度与空间品质。</p></div><div class=\"pi-cell pi-cell-q2\"><span class=\"pi-cell-tag\">Q1 · 本项目目标象限</span><span class=\"pi-star\">★</span><h3>功能合规 × 文化生态升级</h3><p>同时满足国家规范的功能性底线要求与省市层面的文化生态品质升级目标，实现合规与卓越的双重达标。</p></div><div class=\"pi-cell pi-cell-q3\"><span class=\"pi-cell-tag\">Q4 · 基础门槛</span><h3>基础功能满足</h3><p>仅达到建筑规范、消防安全、无障碍等国家强制标准的最低要求，缺乏品质提升与地域特色。</p></div><div class=\"pi-cell pi-cell-q4\"><span class=\"pi-cell-tag\">Q3 · 国家标准驱动</span><h3>功能合规保障</h3><p>《文化馆建设标准》《公共图书馆建设标准》等国标明确面积指标、功能配置、结构安全与节能要求。</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"pi-bottom\"><div class=\"pi-conclusion\"><h4>设计推导结论</h4><p>本项目需在严格满足国家标准功能底线的基础上，积极响应湖北省及十堰市文化生态发展规划，将传统工业文脉、自然山水特质融入建筑设计，实现<strong>功能合规</strong>与<strong>文化生态升级</strong>的双轨并行。</p></div></div><svg style=\"position:absolute;top:0;right:0;width:320px;height:320px;opacity:0.06;z-index:1;pointer-events:none\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 320\"><circle cx=\"320\" cy=\"0\" r=\"280\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"var(--color-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><circle cx=\"320\" cy=\"0\" r=\"220\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"var(--color-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><circle cx=\"320\" cy=\"0\" r=\"160\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"var(--color-primary)\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/></svg><svg style=\"position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;width:200px;height:200px;opacity:0.05;z-index:1;pointer-events:none\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 200\"><rect x=\"10\" y=\"10\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"var(--color-accent)\" stroke-width=\"1\" rx=\"8\"/><rect x=\"30\" y=\"30\" width=\"140\" height=\"140\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"var(--color-accent)\" stroke-width=\"0.7\" rx=\"6\"/></svg><div class=\"pi-deco-line\"></div></div>",
